{"type":"message","id":"e96f6f87","parentId":"bbf0b5f3","timestamp":"2026-03-20T12:14:21.912Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-20 20:14:02 GMT+8] Exec completed (wild-blo, code 0) :: 动态与市场观察** - **AIOps市场规模扩张**：随着企业对系统可靠性和效率需求提升，智能运维成为核心基础设施，市场规模持续增长，但行业更注重技术落地而非概念炒作，呈现“理性降温”与“场景化深耕”特征。 - **厂商技术布局**：华为等头部企业通过发布AI-Native方案、确定性运维体系等，强化技术领先优势，推动行业标准升级。 #### **四、A…\n\nNote: The previous agent run was aborted by the user. Resume carefully or ask for clarification.\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Friday, March 20th, 2026 — 8:14 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-20 12:14 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774008861905}}
